:0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"強烈要求向太幫佢籌款，何君堯，梁美芬幫佢地再搞撐警集會，大叫屌晒你地ICAC老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308b84e378c543970b832a9bcbde4340056ac4ff","tid":446414,"uid":52068,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵十幾萬一個月仲貪</blockquote><br />\n唔係錢嘅問題，而係失去作為一個人嘅基本品格"},{"pid":"caea5ed84d5e5177fefb8f5aec06e807e2a98118","tid":446414,"uid":122635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:07:50.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n<br />\n涉收黑幫賄免費嫖妓 被捕O記高級督察為港大尖子<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170126/56226676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170126%2F56226676&d=1NZAhb25l1WoeQK%2FM0wu7f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4582730e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170126%2F56226676&h=bd0cb395\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20170126/56226676</a><br />\n<br />\n警隊參與國際刑警打擊有組織罪行會議<br />\n有組織罪案及三合會調查科總警司陳樂榮於十一月二十四日至二十五日，率領警司何振東、高級督察陳嘉健，以及商業罪案調查科警司陳國豪和高級督察陳國偉，出席國際刑警組織在泰國曼谷舉行的「第十七次亞太區有組織犯罪專家組會議」。會議由派駐法國里昂國際刑警組織總部的警司呂智豪與泰國警方統籌，他亦有出席會議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1078/chi/4818.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1078%2Fchi%2F4818.html&d=1NZAhb25l1WoeQK%2FM0wu7f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=025ec414\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1078/chi/4818.html</a>"},{"pid":"3f9fbed7a9af929b4bbff9edb5ccba1a7e102b86","tid":446414,"uid":140949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote